From 2016 to 2025/2026, I would like to thank everyone who has been part of this journey.

Throughout the CSGO - CS2 era, everyone had an impact on me, whether it was good or bad. Still, I want to thank everyone for everything.

I am releasing all the plugins I have created over the years as open source. I haven't followed CS2 for a long time, so I don't know whether these plugins still work or not. The only thing I ask is that you do not present these plugins as if they were your own. I leave that decision to your own character and integrity..
